    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend a spell slot to deal &amp;reference[Radiant] damage and attempt to blind the target, in addition to the weapon's damage.</p><p><strong>Constitution Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 4d6 radiant]] damage* and is &amp;reference[Blinded].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> [[/damage 4d6 radiant]] damage, no other effect.*</p></li></ul><p></p><p>*<strong>Using Higher Level Spell Slots</strong> : Damage increases by [[/damage 1d6 radient]]{1d6} for each spell level above 3rd.</p>",
